&lt;h2 class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qovwiyz82zz65zz72zz78zz122zz88zz69zhyfc0z71zytz87zz79zz65zosqfcfkz80zne&quot;&gt;Own and drive technical outcomes across multiple teams and organizations, delivering company critical customer and business impact at scale.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qovwiyz82zz65zz72zz78zz122zz8

&lt;h2 class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;Role Description&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotv4z67zz122zz73zz80zz81z2z68zz89zmz90z511hmfz75z5yr0fa4cfz69zfb&quot;&gt;As a Senior Client Platform Engineer focused on CorpFleet Engineering, you will play a key role in shaping and operating Dropbox’s Windows endpoint platform. You will drive high-impact work across Windows endpoint management, platform reliability, security and compliance-driven improvements, operational automation, and cross-functional platform delivery. This role is centered on preserving and advancing senior ownership of the Windows endpoint area while helping improve how CorpFleet delivers scalable, reliable, and secure endpoint experiences for Dropboxers. You’ll have the opportunity to shape the long-term direction of Windows endpoint engineering at Dropbox while improving the daily experience and security posture of a critical internal platform.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotv4z67zz122zz73zz80zz81z2z68zz89zmz90z511hmfz75z5yr0fa4cfz69zfb&quot;&gt;You will work across partner teams including CorpInfra, IAM, Security, Corp IT, and support teams to define right-sized technical solutions, improve operational quality, and help clarify long-term ownership boundaries across endpoint and Corp Infrastructure-adjacent responsibilities. This is a strong fit for a senior engineer who enjoys ambiguous platform problems, values operational excellence, and wants to influence both technical direction and team effectiveness without moving into people management.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotv4z67zz122zz73zz80zz81z2z68zz89zmz90z511hmfz75z5yr0fa4cfz69zfb&quot;&gt;Own and advance CorpFleet’s Windows endpoint platform, including policy, management, reliability, and operational quality.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotv4z67zz122zz73zz80zz81z2z68zz89zmz90z511hmfz75z5yr0fa4cfz69zfb&quot;&gt;Maintain and improve Windows endpoint management workflows, including Intune-related administration and device lifecycle processes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotv4z67zz122zz73zz80zz81z2z68zz89zmz90z511hmfz75z5yr0fa4cfz69zfb&quot;&gt;Drive security and compliance-related platform work, including application controls, privileged-access-related workflows, secrets-handling patterns, and endpoint visibility.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotv4z67zz122zz73zz80zz81z2z68zz89zmz90z511hmfz75z5yr0fa4cfz69zfb&quot;&gt;Partner with CorpInfra, IAM, Security, Corp IT, and support teams on rollout planning, escalation paths, access dependencies, and ownership boundaries.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotv4z67zz122zz73zz80zz81z2z68zz89zmz90z511hmfz75z5yr0fa4cfz69zfb&quot;&gt;Improve operational scalability through automation, documentation, runbooks, and better platform management practices.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotv4z67zz122zz73zz80zz81z2z68zz89zmz90z511hmfz75z5yr0fa4cfz69zfb&quot;&gt;Lead cross-functional, multi-phase platform initiatives and make sound tradeoff decisions across reliability, security, employee experience, and team capacity.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotv4z67zz122zz73zz80zz81z2z68zz89zmz90z511hmfz75z5yr0fa4cfz69zfb&quot;&gt;Mentor teammates and raise the bar on technical judgment, documentation quality, and operational execution.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt

